          "vnum": 71024,
          "name": "Barren Courtyard",
          "description": "An uneven ring of light brown stones dominates this section of the courtyard, encircling a shallow well. Small blocks of the brown stone, broken in ages past from the top of the well, intermingle with pieces of red stone and shards of tile on the hard earth. A doorway opens into a low building to the east, and the courtyard continues to the south.",
