        "71025": {
          "vnum": 71025,
          "name": "Ashen Remains",
          "description": "Grey ash coats everything in this room: the shattered floor tiles, the broken desks and chairs, the mangled sconces hanging from the walls. Black streaks show through the ash in some places, forming arcane symbols and obscene caricatures. A hallway opens to the south, and a doorway to the west permits access to the courtyard.",
