        "71030": {
          "vnum": 71030,
          "name": "Tumbled Archway",
          "description": "A breach in the wall permits your entry into the ruins. In passing through, you notice a large, trapezoidal stone lying just inside the entry. The stone was perhaps once the keystone of an arch. A courtyard opens to the north, stripped of any ornamentation it might once have boasted. The doorway of a fallen tower opens to the east, and to the south are the infinite grasslands.",
