          "vnum": 71031,
          "name": "Fallen Tower",
          "description": "The shattered remains of the tower cover the floor of this small room, forcing you to pick your way between the smaller stones and to climb over the larger ones. Precariously balanced between one wall and a tall pile of broken stone, a broad slab blocks out the sky. The space is very cramped, and the only exit lies back to the west.",
